- Yo.
You forgot your lunch.

48
00:02:05,542 --> 00:02:07,108
- Oh.
Thank you, Diaz.

49
00:02:07,152 --> 00:02:08,849
- Sir, I didn't realize you
were still staying at Rosa's.

50
