I thought couple's counseling
was going well.

51
00:02:10,373 --> 00:02:11,591
- Not anymore.

52
00:02:11,635 --> 00:02:12,636
At Kevin's request,
I offered to reduce

53
00:02:12,679 --> 00:02:14,377
my work hours by 26%.

54
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,639
Kevin countered with 50.

55
00:02:15,682 --> 00:02:16,944
Which I countered with 30.

56
00:02:16,988 --> 00:02:18,119
Then Kevin says 40—

57
00:02:18,163 --> 00:02:19,686
- Seems like a lot
of math for therapy.

58
00:02:19,730 --> 00:02:21,514
- That's what
Dr. Cheryl said...

59
00:02:21,558 --> 00:02:23,516
which is why we fired her,

60
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,170
and now we're working
with Dr. Ramanujan.

61
00:02:25,213 --> 00:02:28,086
He's a physicist with a nice,
concrete worldview.

62
00:02:28,129 --> 00:02:30,610
Anyway, Kevin refuses
to budge from 36%.

63
00:02:30,654 --> 00:02:33,221
And I'm starting to worry
that I might lose to him.

64
00:02:33,265 --> 00:02:34,397
- You mean lose him.

65
